text: Bryson Djuan Tiller (born January 3, 1993), is an American singer, songwriter, and rapper from Louisville, Kentucky. He started his career in 2011, releasing the debut mixtape titled Killer Instinct Vol.1. In 2015, Tiller signed a record deal with RCA Records. In October of the same year, Tiller released his first album, Trapsoul. His sophomore album, True to Self, was released in May 2017. ==Discography== Studio albums * Trapsoul (2015) * True to Self (2017) Mixtapes * Killer Instinct Vol.1 (2011) == References == Category:Living people Category:1993 births
